title: Sprill and Ritchie Adventures In Time - New HOG Puzzle - Wendy99
description: Sprill and Ritchie are back in an all-new, time-tripping adventure that will tickle your funny bone as much as it teases your brain! Having escaped alien captivity in the Bermuda Triangle, Sprill must now survive his best friend's outlandishexperiments, which sends a temporal whirlwind ripping through time and mixing up items from different ages.
